{"tid":1524612,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"1967年8月24日發生咗一件事","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:29:53.000Z","uid":150100,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"36373d4f10a2fc73dceb3ea190ebe69d7458e742","tid":1524612,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"1967年8月24日上午8時45分，林彬駕駛着車牌號碼AF7268的私家車於何文田窩打老道山文運道開車返回電台，剛轉入文福道近文運道處，被兩名偽裝成修路工人的兇徒攔截。兇徒向車上潑以汽油縱火，林彬全身着火，翌日於伊利沙伯醫院逝世，終年37歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feeb609d3b429e951e5ea30dff7b244d46833df8","tid":1524612,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都一樣，係無差別攻擊！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c31704bc60a504e34e2c941739a7a3c926dc1e66","tid":1524612,"uid":150100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:42:42.000Z","msg":"林彬當時被擲汽油彈，滾出車後再被淋電油，臉部燒焦，頭髮燒光<br />\n<br />\n但願香港唔好再發生類似事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77b